’Ů@eb12109470f1ef52bc89e6f9cfda0c2c9e335d34f133bf555e25b777412bad2aŮűTitle: title: plugin add
Path: Flags
Content:
``--plugin-config {path}``
: Use a plugin registry file other than the one set in 
``$nu.plugin-path``
.
``--shell, -s {path}``
: Use an additional shell program (cmd, sh, python, etc.) to run the plugin.
